  <trk>
    <name>ATH-L1 — Peloponnese Weekend Loop — Day 2</name>
    <desc>Deploy from ATH and ride into the Peloponnese. Hit Corinth Canal Viewpoint — 75m and Nafplio. Loop back to ATH over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
